title: Celtic Thunder - The Very Best Of Celtic Thunder (2015) {FLAC}
description:
Celtic Thunder
The Very Best Of Celtic Thunder (2015)





allmusic.com...

A single-disc collection of the internationally renowned vocal group's biggest and best-loved ensemble numbers, Very Best of Celtic Thunder gathers up 20 songs, including seven newly updated versions of Celtic Thunder classics like "Heartland," "Ireland's Call," "Danny Boy," and "The Galway Girl" along with U2's "I Still Haven't Found What I'm Looking For," which feature the group's most current cast members Colm Keegan and Emmett O'Hanlon. The LP also includes fan favorites like "A Place in the Choir," "Seven Drunken Nights," "The Rocky Road to Dublin," and their stirring take on Paul McCartney's "Mull of Kintyre."
